%% Client-mode search + pagination (useClientList)
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Admin User
    participant Toolbar as AdminTableToolbar
    participant List as useClientList
    participant Src as reactive source[]<br/>(brand/mfr/tag store)
    participant Pipe as computed pipeline<br/>filter → sort → paginate
    participant DT as DataTable

    Note over User,DT: INITIAL LOAD (source owned by store)
    List->>Src: onMounted → store.fetch*()
    activate Src
    Src-->>List: loading / error (passthrough refs,<br/>originate in the store, NOT the composable)
    Src->>Src: source[] populated
    deactivate Src
    Src-->>Pipe: source[] reactive dependency
    Pipe-->>DT: initial page rendered

    Note over User,DT: SEARCH PATH (debounced, in-memory)
    User->>Toolbar: keystroke
    Toolbar->>List: setSearch(term)
    List->>List: search.value = term
    Note right of List: debounce 200ms
    List->>Pipe: invalidate computed
    activate Pipe
    Pipe->>Pipe: 1. filter by searchFields<br/>2. apply filterPredicates<br/>3. sort<br/>4. slice for current page
    Pipe->>Pipe: pagination = buildPagination()<br/>(shared util)
    Pipe-->>DT: re-render (no network call)
    deactivate Pipe

    Note over User,DT: PAGINATION PATH (immediate, in-memory)
    User->>Toolbar: click page n
    Toolbar->>List: setPage(n)
    List->>Pipe: page changed → recompute slice only
    Pipe->>Pipe: slice for page n<br/>(filter/sort already memoized)
    Pipe-->>DT: re-render (NO network call)
